Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.12,0:00:03.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, all you viewers out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:07.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're watchin' Fairy Tail, make \Nsure to keep the room nice and bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.18,0:00:09.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and sit back from the screen, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.03,0:00:13.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.64,0:00:18.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We managed to stop the Magic Giant, \Nbut our guild's been destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.66,0:00:23.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,During it all, Master Jose \Nhas come to attack Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.37,0:00:29.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And the battle between Natsu and Gajeel \Nis now reaching its conclusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.22,0:00:53.63,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all right! I'll yell it out countless times.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.63,0:00:58.70,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe your every tomorrow will be shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:01.05,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The intersection of all people
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.05,0:01:03.66,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,whose dreams have come true is one point:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.66,0:01:08.29,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Never giving up.  And that's why we're not gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:13.47,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,When it seems like you'll be blown away by the headwinds,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.47,0:01:15.62,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,grasp this hand, try to take a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.62,0:01:18.89,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're not alone anymore, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.01,0:01:24.00,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Go forward, more and more!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:26.52,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up on your awesome dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.52,0:01:27.78,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:29.25,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Move on, my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.25,0:01:31.63,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, with the light shining down upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.63,0:01:33.71,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even think about something like giving up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.71,0:01:36.14,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you trade being hurt again for strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.14,0:01:41.63,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes, always looking straight ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.63,0:01:45.91,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,can surely see the light!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.84,0:02:03.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.05,0:02:04.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:07.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.45,0:02:08.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.69,0:02:10.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The shades are still coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.82,0:02:13.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... Even if our \Nguild's been destroyed...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:15.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our fight isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.85,0:02:18.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.79,0:02:23.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:28.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to pay you back for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.39,0:02:31.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you that picking a fight \Nwith Fairy Tail was a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.07,0:02:37.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.18,0:02:38.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:41.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hard Fist of the Iron Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.01,0:02:51.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am... the strongest...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:53.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.24,0:02:56.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blazing Fire Dragon Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.56,0:03:05.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is for Levy, Jet, Droy, \NNab, Macao, Gramps, Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:07.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Lucy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:16.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is for destroying our guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:25.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Al, that light!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:26.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.07,0:03:37.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:38.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:40.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.87,0:03:42.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.64,0:03:44.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:47.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu won!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:51.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That d-damn... tra...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:54.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... we're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:03:59.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.69,0:04:07.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move right now... 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.61,0:04:14.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.18,0:04:18.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You really overdo it, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:20.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye! He's Natsu all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.67,0:04:28.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But... that was kinda cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.92,0:04:32.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:33.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's on a whole 'nother level.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.11,0:04:38.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this... Is this what it means \Nto be a Fairy Tail wizard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.58,0:04:39.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:40.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:42.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevermind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.82,0:04:51.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our dragons have run quite amuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:58.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem like you accounted \Nfor Natsu's battle strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.60,0:05:03.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He is just as powerful than I, if not moreso!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:08.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough with the modesty, Titania Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:12.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your magical power is indeed amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.06,0:05:17.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have never met a wizard who could \Nhold out against me for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.87,0:05:25.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't taken damage from Jupiter, \NI suspect we may have had a better match.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:35.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand Makarov having a wizard \Nthis powerful in his or any other guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:44.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand why I didn't \Nfinish Makarov off before?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:51.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.34,0:06:01.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was to put him in despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:14.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When he wakes up and sees his beloved guild and his \Nbeloved guild members destroyed... How will he feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:18.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crestfallen, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:29.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll destroy that man with despair and \Nsadness never-ending. I will not let him rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:34.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll suffer, and suffer, and suffer \Nsome more... 'Till the end of his days!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:36.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.43,0:06:42.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom Lord was always the number 1 guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:50.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We had the most powerful magic, the most \Ntalented people, and the most money in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:55.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But in these past few years Fairy \NTail has suddenly gotten powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:59.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, Laxus, Mystogan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.76,0:07:05.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those names were heard even in our city, and \Nrumors of Salamander spread throughout the country. {well, the Salamander ones weren't _good_ rumors, you know... Mainly that he destroys crap}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:11.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And at some point suddenly Phantom Lord and Fairy \NTail became the {\i1}two{\i0} signature guilds of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:15.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:19.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially when your guild \Nwas once crappy and weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:20.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.26,0:07:28.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you started this war \Nall because of some petty jealousy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.60,0:07:30.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jealousy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:31.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:34.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to show everyone our superiority!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:38.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a... What a worthless reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:08:04.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've long had a distaste for your guild, so \Nthe trigger to go to war was but a trifle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:11.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A request to return the first \Ndaughter of the Heartfilia Konzern.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.44,0:08:12.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:17.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A daughter of one of the richest \Nfamilies in the country in Fairy Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.34,0:08:22.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How big must you get \Nbefore you're satisfied?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.03,0:08:27.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you bastards can use the Heartfilia's money as you wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.24,0:08:31.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no mistaking that you could gain power greater than ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:34.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That, I cannot allow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.50,0:08:42.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Making such a big deal about \Nwho's on top... It's pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.67,0:08:47.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's your lack of information \Ngathering that's laughable!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:48.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:50.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy ran away from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:52.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think she uses her family's money?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:55.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She lives in a rented house \Nfor 70,000 jewel a month!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:08:59.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She does jobs and fights, together with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:01.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We laugh together...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:02.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cry together...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:04.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a wizard like any other in the guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.28,0:09:07.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I still want to be in the guild...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:10.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I love Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:14.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A trigger for war?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:17.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd rather die than sell out our friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:21.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The daughter of the Heartfilia family?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:26.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As a flower cannot choose the place it \Nblooms, neither can a child choose their parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:43.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A fiend like you knows nothing of \NLucy's tears! You can't know her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.22,0:09:46.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll learn soon enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.99,0:09:51.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you seriously think I'd just \Nhand her over to her father?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.85,0:09:55.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If she doesn't have any \Nmoney, I'll keep her...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:10:00.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get the entire Heartfilia fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:02.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:06.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.28,0:10:08.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll just cause you to suffer more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:19.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, shall we start the horror show?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:23.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's show how you're doing \Nto the rest of Fairy Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:25.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Titania, so full of pride...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:31.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If they see your pitiful state, the \Nrest of the trash are sure to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:33.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Does your wretchedness know no bounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:37.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be looking pretty \Nwretched yourself in a moment. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:45.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm a liability to the guild, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.59,0:10:54.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is up to you... Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:16.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:41.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Much blood has been spilled. {except actually, no, there's been no blood. :)}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:43.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Children's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:50.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of their parent's failure, the \Nchildren have suffered and shed tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.55,0:11:56.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of this, you and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.54,0:12:01.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We must put this to an end!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:07.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.60,0:12:18.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You wish to cause a disaster?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:29.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's for the sake of my guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.91,0:13:03.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The wood... The land... The \Nsky... They are frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.48,0:13:07.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:08.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...I hate humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.84,0:13:13.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Such foolish creatures, always \Nspinning tales of battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:15.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Makarov, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:18.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to die so bad, \Njust croak on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:29.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystogan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:32.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,May I have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:35.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:39.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I had thought it odd how quickly \NMakarov was able to recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:43.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was you who went and collected \NMakarov's magical power, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:46.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never said you could have it! {changing joke a bit.  Plus... He can eat through his mask?  Impressive}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:50.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The war will soon be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:55.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to say anything \Nto encourage more human war,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:13:58.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but you're one of Makarov's friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:14:00.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should leave here and go...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:02.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been off fighting \Non your own, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.46,0:14:14.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom's flags?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:19.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Did he go around crushing each \Nof Phantom's branches on his own?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:25.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,May I have another apple?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.43,0:14:28.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better pick up this \Ntrash before you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:32.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:36.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've given up on you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:40.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Such power can only give birth to sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:46.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And inside the fierce maelstrom, the \Nrage makes one forget the sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.59,0:14:55.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish to believe in a righteous light \Nthat encompasses the rage and sadness...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:15:00.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The righteous light which guides all things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:23.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this warm, familiar magical power?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:34.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone get away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:37.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:38.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.38,0:15:40.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do as he says!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.70,0:15:44.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:46.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:47.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-chan, can you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.91,0:15:52.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you are here, I have \Nno need for the small-fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:55.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'll finish \Nthem off later, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:59.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll only get in his way by being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.32,0:16:01.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave everything to the master!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.64,0:16:08.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been 6 years since we've \Nlast faced each other, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:14.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And Fairy Tail has grown \Nso much in that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:17.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's been destroyed now, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:22.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A guild is not a building. \NIt's a union between people!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:25.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:30.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I get to establish the order of \Nsuperiority among the wizard saints
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:34.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I really owe everything to my \Nkids! You've all done well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:38.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be proud to be part of Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.13,0:16:46.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:46.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.03,0:16:48.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.16,0:16:50.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The ground is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.04,0:16:50.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An earthquake?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.64,0:16:51.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.63,0:17:04.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dead Wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:30.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:31.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:33.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:39.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Gramps' magic, no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:47.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.16,0:17:50.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Such magical power, and yet so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:54.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You do have what it takes to \Nbear the title of Wizard Saint.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:18:01.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had used that power for good and became\Na role-model for the younger generation,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.46,0:18:06.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you would have led the\Nmagic world to its future...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:09.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lecturing me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:17.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As is Fairy Tail tradition, I shall count \Nto three before rendering judgment upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.59,0:18:21.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Beg for mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.26,0:18:27.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.45,0:18:31.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered what you'd say. But this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:33.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Beg for mercy?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:35.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:40.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You expect the number-one guild \Nin the country to bow down to {\i1}you{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:41.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't kid yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.71,0:18:44.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can fight toe-to-toe with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.02,0:18:47.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I won't hold back, so \NI'm actually more powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.84,0:18:49.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:52.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who should beg for mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:53.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Begone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.60,0:18:58.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear with your brats into \Nthe ranks of history, Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:00.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Time's up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:04.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Die, Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:16.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Law is invoked!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.10,0:19:36.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this light?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.42,0:19:37.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So bright...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.81,0:19:41.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The shades are...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:43.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Only they are disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.92,0:19:46.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.23,0:19:48.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But nothing's happening to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.01,0:19:50.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This light... is compassionate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.56,0:19:52.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Fairy Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:54.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Law?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:58.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Righteous light that slays the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:20:02.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It slays only that which the \Ncaster believes is the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.42,0:20:08.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a super-powerful magic, \Nnow counted as legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.87,0:20:39.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never come near Fairy Tail again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:44.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The council will not stay silent \Nafter things have gotten so flashy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.24,0:20:47.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should watch out for \Nyour own skin for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.33,0:20:49.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And same for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.42,0:20:53.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The sadness...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:20:56.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's wide open, just like the last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:58.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.69,0:21:10.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over! The battle of \Nthe guilds is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:18.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you try anything more, I'll "clean \Nyou out," and leave not a trace...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.59,0:21:23.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take Jose with you and go home! Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:28.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yipee! We beat Phantom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.36,0:22:04.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This victory is not from just my power,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.43,0:22:09.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but a victory for our whole family.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.54,0:22:19.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you could do it, Gramps...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.38,0:24:00.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, so why did Jose grab Lucy anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.72,0:24:05.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno. He had a kind of \Ndirty look on his face...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.09,0:24:07.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he had the hots for her or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.54,0:24:09.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are people in the world with \Nfreaky tastes like that, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.58,0:24:11.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd be interested in Lucy, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.37,0:24:14.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well there's Loke, that's one at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.23,0:24:16.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: My Resolve! {it just dawned on me, but the title of this episode is "Atashi no Ketsu(i)" On purpose maybe?}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.85,0:24:20.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about Lucy's future.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.14,0:24:21.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're worried now? She's a lost cause...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.03,0:24:25.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, you're cold as ice.
